"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家繼續幫手文宣 各自爬山 山頂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8054c618044024c2af0ed0b55c46cb5816c91821","tid":1352540,"uid":276715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T21:20:58.000Z","msg":"入得元朗 一定要full gear<br />\n唔好拖隊友後腳<br />\n熟讀路線圖 唔好入小巷<br />\n呢場硬仗黎"},{"pid":"8a2b59f2fa5fcb5c292bd243768e7450618c4e9d","tid":1352540,"uid":260139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T21:30:22.000Z","msg":"如果你選擇沉默 姐係應同佢地既暴力<br />\n唔好再妖魔化呢班人 講撚到佢地戰狼300咁<br />\n更何況香港根本唔應該有呢個文化<br />\n而家元朗獨立左？"},{"pid":"aa698fe39291d6f78ddc76a850d678ce9ee8755b","tid":1352540,"uid":265951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T21:32:13.000Z","msg":"同意，係都係搞何妖先，羞辱條L樣"},{"pid":"bffd343c47dcaf18be88bb0784accacb5028e3fd","tid":1352540,"uid":50310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8a2b59f2fa5fcb5c292bd243768e7450618c4e9d","tid":1352540,"uid":260139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T21:30:22.000Z","msg":"如果你選擇沉默 姐係應同佢地既暴力<br />\n唔好再妖魔化呢班人 講撚到佢地戰狼300咁<br />\n更何況香港根本唔應該有呢個文化<br />\n而家元朗獨立左？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T21:50:42.000Z","msg":"圍村仲有養鬥犬<br />\n班差佬忌佢幾分總有啲嘢<br />\n不過人多就唔同，動物一樣會縮<br />\n<br />\n既然法治唔告佢哋 傷19既<br />\n咁就唔好講笑啦！<br />\n再者，最終你要面對解放軍<br />\n遲早問題，鄉黑都過唔到<br />\n真係食蕉算啦！"},{"pid":"a8e02be7598e3a9dfa9624395afaec3eaf98e32c","tid":1352540,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T21:57:06.000Z","msg":"所有手足唔該睇下呢個topic先？諗點行動<br />\n[反警黑大遊行] 朋友話，今舖要全港反警黑勾結大遊行，拉全建制派落水一齊玩完<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aasoNgU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">htt